Package no.ntnu.idatg1002.budgetapplication.backend

Enum Class ExpenseCategory

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<ExpenseCategory>
no.ntnu.idatg1002.budgetapplication.backend.ExpenseCategory
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<ExpenseCategory>, Constable
public enum ExpenseCategory extends Enum<ExpenseCategory>
Represents the categories for expenses in the budget application. The enum includes the categories housing, transportation, food, utilities, clothing, healthcare, insurance, other, and energy.
